  "action_title": "Breed for resistance traits",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n  \n\nA replicated, controlled study in\u00a0Norway\u00a0found increased survival levels in salmon exposed to infectious pancreatic necrosis when the family was bred for high resistance to the disease compared to a family bred for low resistance to the disease."
}

